title: Can someone help me identify this font ?
content:
![](http://web.archive.org/web/20090714142634im_/http:/typophile.com/files/0518P_website%203_Page_1_5930.png)
  
This is a bit of a tough one. Would really appreciate some help I’ve tried everywhere.

author: mark75

comments.content: Looking at the x-height I’d rather say it’s ITC Lubalin Graph.

I agree with Jan, looks like Lubalin Graph, perhaps demi-weight.

[ITC Lubalin Graph Demi](http://web.archive.org/web/20090714142634/http:/new.myfonts.com/fonts/linotype/itc-lubalin-graph/demi/)
